Xixibase

http://code.google.com/p/xixibase/

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Dependencies:
   -- boost, http://www.boost.org/

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Building Xixibase server
Windows:
Microsoft Visual Studio 2008
1. download boost from http://www.boost.org/
2. create 3rd/boost folder
  xixibase--3rd--boost
          --client
	  --src
3. upzip the boost to 3rd/boost
4. bootstrap.bat
5. bjam release threading=multi link=static
6. build.bat or (Open xixibase.sln with "Microsoft Visual Studio 2008" and build it).

Linux/Mac:
1. download boost from http://www.boost.org/
2. create 3rd/boost folder
  xixibase--3rd--boost
          --client
	  --src
3. upzip the boost to 3rd/boost
4. bootstrap.bat
5. bjam release threading=multi link=static
6. go to src folder and make it.

